            </a>
            <p class="mt-6 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);">
              Connecting CEOs and entrepreneurs for high-signal conversations in New York City.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-16">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-mono text-[10px] font-700 tracking-[0.2em] uppercase" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);">Event</h4>
              <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3">
                <li><a href="#about" class="text-sm transition-opacity hover:opacity-70" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="#team" class="text-sm transition-opacity hover:opacity-70" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);">Team</a></li>
              </ul>
